data.description: Prepare to be captivated by this previously renovated single-story Santee residence. Upon entering, be mesmerized by the exquisite fixtures leading you to a warm living space centered around a charming brick fireplace. The kitchen exudes elegance with its designer white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, and a stylish backsplash. Throughout the home, revel in the allure of wood laminate flooring, modern lighting, and impeccably designed bathrooms. The bedrooms are equipped with ceiling fans for comfort, while the master bathroom boasts a luxurious rainfall shower. Step into the private backyard and enjoy the tranquil view overlooking the canyon. This is an opportunity not to be missed – come and discover the allure of this remarkable home!
